         class="px-5 py-2.5 border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 font-medium transition-colors">
        Отмена
      </a>
    </div>
